BAFO said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 13.43% to NT$9,176,000 from NT$10,599,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             9,176            10,599    
YOY%             -13.43%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             40,445           25,156    
YOY%              60.78% 
